list.name: Save/Read Lists From Files
list.comment: Save/Read Lists From Files Added methods to tracker to read/write list of flavors that comprise a list. Created table model for list selection. Added buttons/menus to App to use new functionality.

changelist.name: Fix recipe calculations for max VG

task.summary: Removed IDE and program files from repository.
Set PG/VG ratio when making a flavor instead of through config.properties file
Added check to calculateMlPgToAdd to handle case where pgProportion is 0. Used a DecimalFormat object to limit significant digits after decimal point in makeRecipeView.
Added method to Tracker class that calculates the molecular weight of the nicotine solution stored in config.properties on startup. Refactored make recipe view to use SpringLayout.
Placed JTables inside JScrollPanes to allow the sort order to be changed by clicking on column headers.

Added new property: amount of liquid remaining before it is added to the auto generated shopping list. Added functionality that allows a user to view a listing of all flavors below a certain amount as a shopping list.
refactored Tracker.buildAutoShoppingList to use stream API
Added main menu option to file menu
Added functionality to display the recipes a flavor is used in in the individual flavor detail view.
Added buttons with links to recipes that each flavor is used in in the flavor detail view. Added table selection listener to shopping list view that links table rows to flavor detail views.

Added a warning message at startup if no properties file is detected. The message provides the user with the option to go straight to the preferences view or to the main menu. Had to modify the way the application initializes the GUI to accomplish this.

Added a warning message at startup if no properties file is detected. The message provides the user with the option to go straight to the preferences view or to the main menu. Had to modify the way the application initializes the GUI to accomplish this.

Display PG/VG/Nicotine in Flavor View. Manually added dummy flavors to flavors list before passing to table. These flavors can be identified by their manufacturer (empty string). Minor cleanup of several files.
Added null checks and error messages to list selection listeners on all tables.
Removed project files from git. Added properties to store the path to the flavor/recipe folders. Flavor/recipe files are now located using this property instead of a hardcoded string.
Added properties to store the path to the flavor/recipe folders. Paths edited in the preferences view are now persisted.
